And so in chapter three, verses 14 through 16, it says, so when the people broke camp to cross the Jordan, the priests carrying the ark of the covenant went ahead of them.

11:01.061 --> 11:10.834
Now the Jordan is at fled stage all during harvest, yet as soon as the priests who carry the ark reached the Jordan,

