Jericho is out there, but God knows that Jericho is out there.

12:14.334 --> 12:16.636
And so what does God do for this next generation?

12:16.696 --> 12:22.321
He gives them a big, you know, neon sign that says, I will take care of you.

12:22.742 --> 12:27.246
