15:22.217 --> 15:31.890
And so that's why I believe God demonstrates his power to this new generation, just as he made the Red Sea part, then here he causes

15:32.130 --> 15:37.337
this new generation to see this miracle of the Jordan waters of the Jordan stopping.

15:38.118 --> 15:40.902
You can learn about how faith operates in this chapter, right?

15:41.042 --> 15:44.487
Because God said to the priest, go stand in the river.

15:45.389 --> 15:49.314
If someone tells you or me to go stand in the river, well, what do we think that means?

15:49.895 --> 15:57.065
I mean, to me, if somebody tells me go stand in the river, I think he means go out to the middle of the river and stand.

15:57.606 --> 16:00.690
I'm pretty sure he doesn't mean just put your big toe in the river.

16:01.090 --> 16:05.616
or whatever, he means get out there in the river and stand.

16:07.818 --> 16:16.870
The amazing thing, my friends, is that God did not stop the Jordan until they followed him and walked all the way up to the water.

16:18.592 --> 16:25.721
Now, a lot of times we psych ourselves out before God ever gets a chance to act on our behalf.

16:25.741 --> 16:30.066
