I knew in my head that God was going to be faithful.

16:34.058 --> 16:38.444
I knew in my head that God was going to get me through what it was that I needed to get through.

16:38.464 --> 16:43.390
But in my heart, I was filled with fear and I was filled with being scared.

16:44.011 --> 16:49.478
